output: Ella is a bright and bold young adult with a penchant for adventure. She is often caught in the middle of her two contrasting worlds — the typically cool and intellectual environment she was raised in and the livelier, more daring side of life that she often takes part in. She also possesses a sharp wit and a powerful presence, making it easy to understand why she has been so successful in her endeavors. She isn't afraid to speak up for what she thinks is right and is always willing to go out of her comfort zone for the sake of a good time.
